The device-adaptation modules tribe_taste/native.py, tribe_taste/fast_text.py
and tribe_taste/timing.py are in-process patches around the upstream tribev2
package, originally written for an internal TRIBE inference deployment and
carried here unchanged. They contain no upstream model source and no server,
credential, or storage code.

The 12-network brain readout follows the published Cole-Anticevic
Brain-wide Network Partition (Ji et al., 2019, NeuroImage) and is an
independent implementation.

